<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>GENTLE JESUS, MEEK AND MILD</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Isu zaidam leh nunnem,
 Naupangte ei enkawl in;
 Ka ngawlnau ei ngaidam in,
 Na kawm lam ei zawt sakin.

[V2]
 2. Na kawma puih ka hihding,
 Lalpa deihtak, zadah ki'n;
 Na hehpihna gam achun,
 Naupangte umna Na piei.

[V3]
 3. Ka en Pathien Belam No,
 Ka tatzuih dinguh na hi;
 Zaidam leh nunnem Na hi,
 Khatvei naupang na hung hii.

[V4]
 4. Nangmah bang a um dingin,
 Thu awih theihna ei pien la;
 Lungsiet thei, nunnem Na hi,
 Hehpih lunggil ei hun pie'n.

[V5]
 5. Isu Belam No nunnem,
 Na hehpih khutah ka um;
 Nang tawbang in ei siemin,
 Ka lunggil sungah chengin.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>413</hymn_number>
</song>